{"tid":1252010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開始有人上黎叫人唔好用八達通大搞白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-06-22T18:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T19:56:47.000Z","uid":78492,"like":53,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"54de6e7fc23ae2c6df7157d0ec5c9e5fa2c0881d","tid":1252010,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:44:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1251699/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1251699/page/1</a><br />\n呢個樓主個帳係新既<br />\n第一個POST係69之後出<br />\n至於八達通個POST入邊講既野好多都係唔合理<br />\n係嚇到大家都唔敢用八達通<br />\n從而令到大家出門口都麻煩左<br />\n根本只要唔用平時日常既八達通係唔洗太擔心被追蹤<br />\n1：唔係個人八達通根本無記錄個人資料，發完夢可以退左張八達通<br />\n2：咁多人出街，追蹤得幾多個，同埋用邊條法例告得入<br />\n<br />\n唔好自制白色恐怖<br />\n不退，不散。"},{"pid":"b1d44089f37f074e2b0a08c46a422f3adb5a5e72","tid":1252010,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:47:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"777c79ccbef64320e662554fd492166ff854abf1","tid":1252010,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:48:21.000Z","msg":"可唔可以真係做反次主動！？香港時日冇多啦！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n制度既敗壞先係問題既根本！！！唔想呢次運動失敗既入！<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n【繼續吹】我地只係步緊黃背心後塵！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243981\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243981</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"070610be0da812779e92e31ef93dded791946dc1","tid":1252010,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:51:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f9967c2279469067328c579cc5a616822abf3f9","tid":1252010,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T18:52:12.000Z","msg":"乜野不退不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631c00f79ca95fcd6f